### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/

###

### Get recommendations for user123 (who likes AI and nature)
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "limit": 5,
  "excludeAuthorPosts": true
}

###

### Get recommendations with more results
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "limit": 10,
  "excludeAuthorPosts": false
}

###

### Get recommendations for a new user (should return popular posts)
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "new_user_456",
  "limit": 5,
  "excludeAuthorPosts": true
}

###

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 100,
  "authorId": "test_user",
  "text": "Amazing breakthrough in quantum computing! The future is here.",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Create a LIKE reaction
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/reactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 200,
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1,
  "authorId": "user123",
  "type": "LIKE",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Create a DISLIKE reaction
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/reactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 201,
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 3,
  "authorId": "user123",
  "type": "DISLIKE",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Refresh recommendations cache for user123
POST http://localhost:8000/recommendations/refresh/user123

###

### Recommendations health check
GET http://localhost:8000/recommendations/health

